synonyms.synonym: Down syndrome critical region protein C

protein.specific_function: Part of the complex catalyzing the transfer of N-acetylglucosamine from UDP-N-acetylglucosamine to phosphatidylinositol, the first step of GPI biosynthesis.

go_class.description: preassembly of GPI anchor in ER membrane
